## Dependencies & Building

* SDL
* SDL_ttf
* SDL_image
* SDL_mixer

To compile Woods, simply run `make` in the base directory.



## Controls

* Arrow keys / Joystick D-pad = Move cursor (all directions) / Adjust balance (left and right)
* Z / Joystick Button 0 = Confirm menu selection
* ESC / Joystick Button 9 = Pause the game

